*Resources*

* New feeding guides files [https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1cYbQpXBtuwjGTHd_LVatwnHEw2neQOPNbe8KdMRioKY/edit?gid=755692854#gid=755692854|https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1cYbQpXBtuwjGTHd_LVatwnHEw2neQOPNbe8KdMRioKY/edit?gid=755692854#gid=755692854|smart-link] 
* Update feeding guides instructions: [https://github.com/hellofresh/web/tree/master/toolbox/commands/wl-generate-feeding-guides|https://github.com/hellofresh/web/tree/master/toolbox/commands/wl-generate-feeding-guides|smart-link] 
{panel}

{panel:bgColor=#ffebe6}
*Out of Scope* 

* If applicable, when the task/feature is split into multiple tickets
{panel}

