*Acceptance Criteria* *_(focus on the what, not the how)_*

* PDF feeding guides are mapped based on SKU and portion %
** If user doesn‚Äôt have a pet profile (or NPS is down) it should default to 100% portion
** If mixed plan always assume portion is 100% (see dev info)
* New pdfs are launched
* Implement behind a FF +(Only needed if PDFs aren‚Äôt uploaded yet when this change is made)+
{panel}

